snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 - Mai Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Mai from Fatal Fury promises to warm you up when she bounces in to #StreetFighter6 on February 5. Don't keep her waiting or she'll use her ninja trickery on you.

Mai can be purchased individually with Fighter Coins and the owners of the Year 2 Character Pass / Ultimate Pass will automatically get access to Mai when she releases.

https://streetfighter.com/6/
